ey're selling more pets. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000028><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> cheftako</span><br> <span class=usertitle>Unregistered User</span><br>   <font color=#70DB93>(10/3/03 3:09 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub60.ezboard.com/fcreaturehandlersofswgfrm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Neither fish nor fowl.</span><hr size=1> Either we're a combat class and we make money doing combat. In which case we should be treated as such. Combat related nerfs removed, mission payouts set according to CH level. Otherwise we're not a combat proffession. In that case we're in co-opetition with BE and should definetly be allowed to sell pets. In that case we should be able to put tamed pets for sale on vendors like any other class with a product to sell.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub60.ezboard.com/fcreaturehandlersofswgfrm3.showPrevMessage?topicID=11.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub60.ezboard.com/fcreaturehandlersofswgfrm3.showNextMessage?topicID=11.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub60.ezboard.com/fcreaturehandlersofswgfrm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11.topic&index=5><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/black_default/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub60.ezboard.com/fcreaturehandlersofswgfrm3.emailToFriend?topicID=11.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub60.ezboard.com/fcreaturehandlersofswgfrm3.threadControl?topicID=11.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/them